    "body": "At regular sync we lose a lot of peers because it's too slow to process slot/epoch.\r\n\r\n```\r\n2020-10-30 13:32:14 [SYNC]             info: Peer status activePeers=2, syncPeers=2, unknownRootPeers=2\r\n2020-10-30 13:32:51 [SYNC]             info: Peer status activePeers=2, syncPeers=0, unknownRootPeers=0\r\n2020-10-30 13:33:27 [SYNC]             info: Peer status activePeers=2, syncPeers=0, unknownRootPeers=0\r\n2020-10-30 13:34:04 [SYNC]             info: Peer status activePeers=2, syncPeers=2, unknownRootPeers=2\r\n```\r\n\r\nif I ignore signature verification, I normally get 10-15 sync peers. Hopefully this issue help resolve it.",
